'''Tafrara''' neɣ '''Izik''' d [[akud]] n [[ass|wass]] anda iy beddu [[igenni]] yeččaray d [[tafat]] send n [[alluy|walluy n tfukt]],

Tafrara tettwagzam ar 3 n wannufen (iḥricen), issentay (ibeddu) mi ara ad tili [[tafukt|tfukt]] 18 n tseddaṛin s ddaw n [[igli (tanzagt)|yegli]], Dɣa tayyi d ''tafrara n tallunt'' ur [[asekkud|nettwaskad]] s wallen , maca itran meẓẓiyen ɣellin ur d-ttbanayen ara, Annuf-a yettaǧa-d [[akud|akud-is]] i ''tafrara tawlalt''  mi ara ad tiweṭ tfukt ar 12 n tseddaṛin s ddaw n yegli, deg tallit-a yettwazmer usnefru (imeyyez) n [[tafat]] tamezwarut n tefrara, ɣas akken deg wannuf wis 3 kan (''tafrara taɣarimt'') id tettbin tafat s waṭas, deg tallit-a tafukt tettali-d ar 6 n tseddaṛin s ddaw n yegli

